				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R_\star $$\end{document}, just fills its Roche lobe, whose radius, r⋆Roche\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
