				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$3\, M_\odot $$\end{document} RG star, whose core was replaced by a point mass, and a companion, whose mass was slowly increased to 1M⊙\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
