Rasio and Livio (1996) used up to 50 000 particles to follow the onset of the unstable mass transfer and initial inspiral of a 0.7M⊙\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
